data.description: Seller is open to assist with a rate buydown/closing costs to make this house your clients home. Come check out this beautiful single story home that offers 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths. The kitchen offers granite countertops with plenty of cabinet space and generous countertop work space. The kitchen opens into a large family room area perfect for entertaining. The master bedroom is split from the other three bedrooms, giving the owners their own personal space. Outdoors is ready for entertaining with newly installed artificial turf, an above ground pool and a covered patio. The exterior of the home was just painted in the last month. Come see it today and make it your home!
